  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK612">
<l>viṉaikkaṇ viṉaikeṭa lōmpal viṉaikkuṟai </l>
<l>tīrntāriṟ ṟīrntaṉ ṟulaku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Take care not to give up exertion in the midst of a work the world will abandon those who abandon their unfinished work.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
